Kahuf e toofan hai bijlion ka hai dar, Sakht mushkil he aaqa, kidhar jaayein hum, aap hee gr na leyin gay, hamari khabar, ham museebat k marey kidhar jayein gay! Tajdar e Haram, Tajdar e Haram! 

You were a great Qawwal and person.

If Amjad sabri were alive, I bet this video couldn't gather even 1 lac views,  despite of being uploaded 19 hours ago because the piece isn't appealing at all. Don't know about others, but I personally watched this video In order to have a look on Amjad sabri!!!! RIP Amjad Sabri!
